            <title><![CDATA[大S对媒体证实离婚 汪小菲称不知情]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[<div class="figure-media"><img class="img-fluid lazyload" data-src="/s3/files/styles/article_large_full/public/images/202106/20210605/20210109003697.jpg?itok=7agIKvLb" title="台湾女星大S徐熙媛与丈夫汪小菲，多次被传婚变。（互联网）" alt="台湾女星大S徐熙媛与丈夫汪小菲，多次被传婚变。（互联网）" src="https://www.zaobao.com/s3/files/styles/article_large_full/public/images/202106/20210605/20210109003697.jpg?itok=7agIKvLb" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></div>
